Mahi – Tu Meri Muskaan

Jab se tujhe dekha hai, dil yahi kehne laga,
Har khushi ka matlab bas tu hi ban gaya.
Subah ki pehli roshni, shaam ka sukoon hai tu,
Har dua mein jo maanga tha, woh haseen junoon hai tu.
Rab se bas itni si dua,
Har pal tera ho khushiyon se bhara.
Aaj tera janamdin hai,
Dil yeh geet sirf tere liye gaa raha.
Happy Birthday, Mahi,
Tu meri har khushi ki wajah bani.
Teri hansi mein meri duniya,
Teri baaton mein meri zindagi.
Har saal yun hi muskurana,
Har sapna tera sach ho jaana.
Meri dua hai bas itni si,
Hamesha khush rehna, Mahi.
Chaand bhi tere noor se sharmaaye,
Taare tera naam gungunaaye.
Har nayi manzil tu aasaani se paaye,
Har dua teri Rab kabool kar jaaye.
Agar kabhi udaasi aaye,
Meri muskaan tujhe hasaaye.
Har mod pe saath rahoon,
Dil se bas itna vaada nibhaoon.
Happy Birthday, Mahi,
Aaj ka din hai sirf tera hi.
Khushiyon ki baarish hoti rahe,
Har dua teri poori hoti rahe.
Chaand, taare aur yeh jahaan,
Sab kahe ek hi baat—
Happy Birthday, Mahi... I hope you always keep smiling.